{
  "stem": "7683.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Phosphorus-- something-- some kind of--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some ointment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They can use it, and that helps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I want them to go and buy that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I gave them the gold pen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, take that and bring some ointment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that helped a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- so there was something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always were alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I say, no, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing, when they took us, that we can take some washing ourselves once a month or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we moved down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But otherwise, we didn't move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- what was I going to say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I sometimes snored.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and he hear that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, be careful, because they can hear it, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So Selma always waked me when I was snoring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one day, we had-- we cut through the roof.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We could see there was some place where storks were there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one day, the storks are gone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he cames and tells us, he says, you have to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "If storks go away from a place, that is not a good sign.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we talked him over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We told him, that's OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will come back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of the storks came back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So no matter how they treated us, they saved our life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because how many people did what they did?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I hear later friends that did the same thing-- at night, they killed them and took the money without keeping them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were really lucky.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- When you think back on those months, what do you remember as being-- what do you-- what do you remember most about them?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About what?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
